### labwc autostart
### Place commands here to have programs started on login.

### Current screenlock and suspend options. - CHOOSE ONLY ONE.
##
## Suspend only. (uncomment below)
# swayidle -w timeout 600 'systemctl suspend' &

## 5 minute lockscreen delay. (uncomment below)
# swayidle -w timeout 300 'swaylock -f -e -c 072836 --ring-color 0C5E5B --line-uses-ring' &

## 5 minute lockscreen + 10 minute suspend. (uncomment below)
# swayidle -w timeout 300 'swaylock -f -e -c 072836 --ring-color 0C5E5B --line-uses-ring' timeout 600 'systemctl suspend' &

